v 3
d projectinit v2.1 - Professional Research Project Initializer (Enterprise)
d
d projectinit creates professional, reproducible research project structures
d following J-PAL (MIT), DIME (World Bank), and AEA Data Editor standards.
d
d Features:
d - J-PAL/DIME folder structure with numbered directories
d - LaTeX integration (standard and PUC templates)
d - GitHub automation for version control
d - Bilingual support (English/Spanish)
d - Optimized for Chilean and Peruvian microdata (CASEN, ENAHO)
d - One-click reproducibility infrastructure
d - Dynamic paths using c(pwd) for portability
d
d Distribution-Date: 20260121
d License: MIT
d
d Author: Maykol Medrano
d Email: mmedrano2@uc.cl
d URL: https://github.com/MaykolMedrano/projectinit
d
